creator: MiGym
descriptionHtml:
Equilibrium Fitness is a state-of-the-art 24 Hour Fitness Facility located in New Buffalo, Michigan. We offer membership options for both full-time and part-time residents, and we can customize any of our options for you. We have cardio machines, selectorized weight machines, plate loaded machines, free weights, many supplementary pieces, a private shower room, lockable lockers, complimentary towel service, water cooler, entertainment wall with large tv's, private training studio for one-on-one personal training and classes, and a proxy key entry system with cameras and panic buttons. We have AdvoCare products and Gym Merchandise available for purchase on-site and online. We offer Spin Cycle classes year round, and Group Training Classes in the summer. We also offer one-on-one Personal Training, Partner Training, and Online Personal Training Programs.
Use this App to view our class schedules and sign up for classes, stay up-to-date with any pertinent gym announcements, reach out to a staff member, check-in and share your experiences via Social Media, give us Feedback, purchase AdvoCare supplements or Gym
Merchandise, and keep yourself on track with all of your fitness goals. We look forward to serving you in all of your health and wellness needs!
